title: Sequenom, Inc. Shares 2015 Investor And Analyst Day Presentation
text:
SAN DIEGO, Sept. 28, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Sequenom,   today is hosting its 2015 investor and analyst day in New York, NY.
The presentation, which includes a discussion of the Company's corporate vision and plans for reproductive health and oncology testing, is now available on the "Invest" section of the Sequenom website at www.sequenom.com/invest .
About Sequenom
Sequenom, Inc. ( SQNM ) is committed to enabling healthier lives through the development of innovative products and services. The Company serves patients and physicians by providing early patient management information. To learn how Sequenom is interpreting the genome to improve your life, visit www.sequenom.com .
